] (2026-05-14 14:13):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，今天看起来不会补缺了，缺口上方就企稳反弹了，是不是指数强于预期啊？[/quote]<br/>反而会把后面的涨幅降低", "lou": 2577, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 868056951, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778739259}, {"pid": 868057654, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-14 14:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868057134,45974302,5125]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67145444]sentser[/uid] (2026-05-14 14:15):[/b]<br/><br/>可是狼大，老登股里的银行 保险 电力过的并不差，而且还挺滋润的，老登也分层次的吧[/quote]<br/>电力不是老登 他跟的是算力里面的防御<br/>其他不差在哪里？他们和科技比如何", "lou": 2578, "content_length": 71, "reply_to": 868057134, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778739555}, {"pid": 868058125, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 170, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-14 14:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们是不是有病？", "lou": 2579, "content_length": 16, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778739772}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155491, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109336, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "米璐璐6666LLL", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109357, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,652088